node.text: My world was complete 18 years ago when you were born at 10:20 pm. Watching you grow up into this amazing guy has been such an incredible journey. Being your mom has been the best gift and I will forever be thankful for getting to stay home and raise you. I love you more than words. Happy 18th birthday to my baby boy. #mybabyisallgrownup #heis18 #timegoesbysofast #iwillalwaysloveyou #hehasmyheart #proudmom @paytonmoormeier (look close…we have the same tattoo 🥰)

node.text:
PURE L❤️VE. 
Forever and Always I will be your biggest fan. I am so proud of how hard you worked to get to where you are. I love you. Have fun the next couple weeks - but know I will be missing you. Love you ❤️ @paytonmoormeier

node.text: We don’t meet people by accident There is a purpose for everyone you meet in life. I’m lucky that these two came into my life when they did. My life is better because of them. Everyone deserves true friendships like this. Thank you for the great times and great memories.  @chrisaddario @ktucker1113. Great day started with an unexpected hike toward the Hollywood sign. @bobbykalton we had a fun HOT adventure and looking back I’m so happy we started that hike. We did find the Bat Cave from Batman. Trip out to Malibu and seeing breathtaking views. #funtimes #malibu #mybestfriends #cali #hollywoodsign
